5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alysha_Newman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alysha_Newman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a surprise winner\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"the only athlete\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 547}, {\"ngram\": \"Photo\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"PHOTOSPORT\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 642}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"a countback\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"4.85m.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McCartney exited when the bar was raised to 4.80m, narrowly failing in each of her three attempts.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McCartney\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"4.80m\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"her three attempts\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a disappointing outcome for the 27-year-old who had sailed over on her first attempt at each of her two previous heights - 4.60m and 4.70m.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a disappointing outcome\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"her first attempt\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"her two previous heights\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"4.60m\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"4.70m.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She nevertheless produced her trademark smile after the bar fell for a third time and later said it was because ''you never know whether you are going back again\\\".\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her trademark smile\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"a third time\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eliza McCartney waves farewell after going out of the women's pole vault final at the Paris Olympics.Photo:photosport \\\"I want to be going to LA in four years time but I do not know if it's going to happen.\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eliza_McCartney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eliza McCartney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eliza_McCartney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eliza_McCartney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's pole vault\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"four years\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why would not I just enjoy this moment because it's happening right now and I get to be out there.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this moment\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The atmosphere out there is amazing, it's so special to get these opportunities.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The atmosphere\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"these opportunities\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I just love it.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fact I get to go out there and do my thing,express myself, pole vault which I love to do.\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The fact\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"my thing\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1669}, {\"ngram\": \"pole vault\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How lucky am I, I just love it all.\\\"\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McCartney said was in tears when speaking later to journalists and reflected on her ongoing battle with a variety of injuries, including problems in the leadup to Paris.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1918, \"end\": 1923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999934727839, \"rank\": 6.527266866883694e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McCartney\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"journalists\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"her ongoing battle\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"a variety\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1868}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"problems\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"the leadup\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a really tough preparation, nothing like my indoor season which went really smoothly and beautiful,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really tough preparation\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"my indoor season\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't as prepared as I would have wanted to be, then we made some good decisions in the last month or two to actaully I could get here and pole vault, because that was never guaranteed with me.\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some good decisions\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"the last month\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So to get able to get in a final and come sixth equal, I will absolutely take that.\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My attempts at 4.80 were just not quite it, I think it showed I did not have the right run-in, but I do really believe I gave everything I could today, so you can not ask anything more than that, so I am happy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My attempts\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"quite it\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2374}, {\"ngram\": \"the right run-in\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2425}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olivia McTaggart (L), Imogen Ayris (C) and Eliza McCartney celebrate together after qualifying for the Women's Pole Vault Final at Stade de France during the 2024 Paris Olympics.Photo:Simon Stacpoole / www.photosport.nz Ayris finished 12th and McTaggart 13th after both cleared 4.60m in their first Olympic final appearance but neither could advance when the target was increased by another 10cm.\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2545, \"end\": 2561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_McTaggart\", \"score\": 0.9999992894275034, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olivia McTaggart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_McTaggart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_McTaggart\"}, {\"begin\": 2588, \"end\": 2603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eliza_McCartney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eliza McCartney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eliza_McCartney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eliza_McCartney\"}, {\"begin\": 2735, \"end\": 2744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Stacpoole\", \"score\": 0.9999999868998658, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stacp